     <span class="break"/>from M
     <sub>MR</sub> to VH
     <sub>MR</sub>
    </td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">No special precautions are required: Maintain normal working and hydration procedures.</td>
   </tr>
