     <span class="break"/>H
     <sub>MR</sub> and VH
     <sub>MR</sub>
    </td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Pre-alarm (attention): Pay attention to frequent drinking and plan small breaks.</td>
   </tr>
