     <sub>MR</sub> and VH
     <sub>MR</sub>
    </td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Alarm: Drink frequently and increase the number of breaks with cooling.</td>
   </tr>
